<h2> Nutcracker Design </h2>
<p> <strong>Task:</strong> Design a nutcracker that can crack open a macademia nut by hand using a simple lever. </p>

<p> <strong> Plan: </strong> 
Examine FBD of a nutcracker then take the moment about the front point
</p>

<p> <strong> Given:</strong> 
<ul>
  <li>Nut diameter: 2 cm</li>
  <li>Grip force: 45 kg</li>
  <li>Required cracking force: 222.18 kg</li>
  <li> Assume nut is placed at 3cm</li>
</ul></p>

